name: Summer BBQ or Picnic Invitation Custom for you / Party Printable
description:
Summer BBQ or Picnic Party Invitation / Printable / Custom for you 

Just send me your party information and I will make a custom invitation for you! 

Invitation will measure 5x7 and will be printable in a PDF file. 
There will be 2 invitations to a page PDF. 
You will also receive it in jpeg format 

You can print at home or send it out to your local printer. 
Nothing will be shipped. 
File will be emailed without watermark to email address.

I will need party information 
I will send proof with all your info

name: DiY Printable Bracket Labels aka Printable fancy labels / greens browns blues yellows oranges stripe
description:
Green & Brown Multi colored stripe labels Print on Demand.
Green & Brown Multi colored stripe Fancy Labels PDF

*Place settings
*Name cards
*Gift tags
*scrapbooking
*Party Food Labels

The uses are endless! Size is 8.5 x 11. You will need to cut out labels yourself...you could round corners, add glitter...get creative!

Please note: Nothing will be shipped. You will receive the pdf via email. Recommended printing on at least 65 lb. cardstock.
